    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-80a5-a5f9-d2d390707929",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The work attempts to use OULAD to predict student performance using 3 distinct categories. The Ensemble Model performed better than all other models attempted. The study not only makes predictions but also delves into discussing pedagogical policies and guidelines that can be derived from these early predictions.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-80a5-a5f9-d2d390707929",
